data.description: This charming 3 bed/3 bath that is centrally located in Hot Springs is the perfect place to call home. You’ll love the light & airy floor plan with a spacious living room where the natural light pours in from the large windows creating a warm and inviting atmosphere. The kitchen boasts ample counter space, new stainless steel appliances w/gas cooktop & tons of storage. Primary suite has its own private bathroom. The converted garage has been thoughtfully designed to serve as a versatile mother-in-law suite. Featuring its bathroom, kitchen & living area, this space offers endless possibilities for accommodating guests, extended family members, or even as a home office or studio. The fenced-in backyard offers plenty of space for outdoor activities, gardening, or simply relaxing in the sunshine. Updates include new roof 2023, hot water heater 2021, new flooring 2021.
